# Live YouTube subscriber count on the footer badge.
# Google Cloud console -> enable "YouTube Data API v3" -> create an API key.
# Free at this volume: one channels.list call per hour costs 1 of 10,000 daily units.
# Without this, the badge degrades to a plain Subscribe link with no count.
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=

# Contact form delivery. formspree.io -> new form -> copy the id out of the endpoint
# URL (https://formspree.io/f/<id>). Public by design; it only accepts submissions.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=
